          Salesforce.com product and provide Cloud & Salesforce outsourcing services to small and mid-size businesses
          and large IT vendors.
        </p>
        <br />
        <h3 class="text-lg"><b>Core Strengths</b></h3>
        <ul class="list-disc">
          <li>Extensive & varied SaaS/Cloud Computing consulting experience</li>
          <li>Broad functional footprint to support end-to-end processes</li>
